## 🎯 Design Patterns

### Layout Principles
1. **8px Grid System** - All spacing based on 8px increments
2. **Consistent Margins** - 24px between major sections, 16px between elements
3. **White Space** - Generous padding for breathing room
4. **Responsive Design** - Mobile-first approach

### Interactive States
```css
/* Hover Effects */
.cj-interactive:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
}

/* Focus States */
.cj-focusable:focus {
    outline: none;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.2);
}

/* Loading States */
.cj-loading {
    opacity: 0.7;
    pointer-events: none;
    position: relative;
}

.cj-loading::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    border: 2px solid var(--cj-gray-300);
    border-top: 2px solid var(--cj-primary);
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
}

@keyframes spin {
    to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
}
```

