## ✅ Usage Guidelines

### Do's
- ✅ Use consistent spacing from the 8px grid system
- ✅ Apply hover effects to interactive elements
- ✅ Use semantic color meanings (green for success, red for error)
- ✅ Maintain proper contrast ratios (4.5:1 minimum)
- ✅ Use the established typography scale

### Don'ts
- ❌ Don't use arbitrary spacing values
- ❌ Don't mix different blue shades outside the palette
- ❌ Don't skip focus states for accessibility
- ❌ Don't use more than 3 font weights in a single view
- ❌ Don't create buttons smaller than 44px touch target

